name: Okenya bodycon
description:
A Bodycon dress has the potential for many looks. Great for all occasions. Fits the body comfortably while remaining elegant, professional, and well covered. 

A must have is a mid sleeve Bodycon. This comes in different fabric and colors. A Bodycon can be ordered short, mid thigh, or mid calf. Can be paired with winter trends.
